{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Constructor","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Constructor","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>构造函数</strong>属于被实例化的特定类<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Object\">对象</a> 。构造函数初始化这个对象，并提供可以访问其私有信息的方法。构造函数的概念可以应用于大多数<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/OOP\">面向对象</a>的编程语言。本质上，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> 中的构造函数通常在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Class\">类</a>的实例中声明。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// 这是一个通用的默认构造函数类 Default</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 这是一个带参数声明的重载构造函数类 Overloaded</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Overloaded</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">arg1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> arg2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>argN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>要调用 JavaScript 中类的构造函数，请使用 <code>new</code> 操作符将新的<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Object_reference\">对象引用 <small>(en-US)</small></a>分配给一个<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Variable\">变量 <small>(en-US)</small></a>。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 分配给局部变量 defaultReference 的一个新的 Default 对象引用</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> defaultReference <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本常识","title":"基本常识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>维基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constructor_%28object-oriented_programming%29\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">构造函数</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"技术参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>MDN 上的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/JavaScript/Objects\">JavaScript 面向对象编程中的构造函数</a></li>\n  <li>MDN 上的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/new\">JavaScript 的 New 操作符</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"构造函数属于被实例化的特定类对象 。构造函数初始化这个对象，并提供可以访问其私有信息的方法。构造函数的概念可以应用于大多数面向对象的编程语言。本质上，JavaScript 中的构造函数通常在类的实例中声明。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Constructor","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Constructor","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Constructeur","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Constructor (コンストラクター)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Конструктор","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"建構子","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":